<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <!-- <link rel = "stylesheet" href = "/stylesheets/moodtracker.css">  -->
    <title>mood journal</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/materialize/1.0.0/css/materialize.min.css">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/icon?family=Material+Icons" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        .button-color {
            background-color: rgb(199, 228, 237);
            color: black;
        }
        .button-color:active {
            background-color:  rgb(4, 124, 164);
            color: white;
        }

        .button-color:hover {
            background-color:  rgb(122, 185, 206);
            color: white;
        }

        .button-color.active {
            background-color:  rgb(4, 124, 164);
            color: white;
        }

        body {
            background-color: lightblue; 
        }

        button {
            height: 36px;
            padding-left: 16px;
            padding-right: 16px;
            padding-top: 0px;
            padding-bottom: 0px;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: black;
            margin-top: 0;
            margin-bottom: 20px;    
            border-radius: 2px;
            display: inline-block;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            vertical-align: middle;    
            transition: background-color, 0.15s, color, 0.15;
            background-color: rgb(199, 228, 237);
        }

        .active {
            background-color:  rgb(4, 124, 164);
            color: rgb(149, 0, 0);
        }

        button:active, button.active {
            background-color:  rgb(4, 124, 164);
            color: white;
        }

        button:hover {
            background-color: light
        }

        .answer-choice {
            display:inline-block;
        }

        .home {
            text-align: center;
        }
        .nav-color {
            background-color: rgb(170, 218, 233);
            color: black;
        }
        .custom-margin {
            padding-left: 20px;
        }

    </style>
    <script src="/scripts/mood_journal.js" defer></script>
</head>
<body>
    <nav class = "nav-color center-align">
        <ul>
            <row>
          <li><a class = "black-text col" href ="/home">moodwise</a></li>
          <li><a class = "black-text col" href ="/journaling">journaling</a></li>
          <li><a class = "black-text col" href = "/journaling/viewJournals">view journals</a></li>
          <li><a class = "black-text col" href ="/moodtracker">mood tracker</a></li>
          <!-- <li><a class = "black-text col " href = "/pictureupload">upload your picture!!</a></li> -->
          <li><a class = "black-text col" href = "/todo">to-do</a></li>
          </row>
        </ul>

    </nav>
    <li><strong>user</strong> <%= username %></li>
    <div class = "custom-margin">
        <div class =  "intro">
            <h1 class = "center-align">my mood?</h1>
            <p class = "center-align">if you're struggling to identify how you feel, take this short quiz: we might be able to push you in the right direction!</p>
        </div>
        
        <h4>1. how much sleep did you get last night?</h2>
            <div class = "custom-margin">
                <div class="answer-choice">
                    <button class = "btn button-color" id="q1a1" data-question = "1"> &#60; 3 hours</button>
                </div>
                <div class ="answer-choice">
                    <button class = "btn button-color" id = "q1a2" data-question = "1"> 3 - 5 hours</button>
                </div>
                <div class="answer-choice">
                    <button class = "btn button-color" id="q1a3" data-question = "1"> 6 - 8 hours</button>
                </div>
                <div class="answer-choice">
                    <button class = "btn button-color" id="q1a4" data-question = "1"> &gt; 9 hours</button>
                </div>
            </div>

        <h4>2. is there currently something weighing on your mind? </h2>
            <div class = "custom-margin">
                <div class="answer-choice">
                    <button class = "btn button-color" id="q2a1" data-question = "2"> yes </button>
                </div>
                <div class="answer-choice">
                    <button class = "btn button-color" id="q2a2" data-question = "2"> no </button>
                </div>
            </div>
        
        <h4>3. do you feel like you've been productive with your time lately?</h2>
            <div class = "custom-margin">
                <div class="answer-choice">
                    <button class = "btn button-color" id="q3a1" data-question = "3"> yes </button>
                </div>
                <div class="answer-choice">
                    <button class = "btn button-color" id="q3a2" data-question = "3"> no </button>
                </div>
            </div>

        <h4>4. have you recently been in a fight with someone? </h2>
            <div class = "custom-margin">
                <div class="answer-choice">
                    <button class = "btn button-color" id="q4a1" data-question = "4"> yes </button>
                </div>
                <div class="answer-choice">
                    <button class = "btn button-color" id="q4a2" data-question = "4"> no </button>
                </div>
            </div>

        <h4>5. have there been any big changes in your life lately?</h2>
            <div class = "custom-margin">
                <div class="answer-choice">
                    <button class = "btn button-color" id="q5a1" data-question = "5"> yes </button>
                </div>
                <div class="answer-choice">
                    <button class = "btn button-color" id="q5a2" data-question = "5"> no </button>
                </div>
            </div>
        <h4>6. are you taking this quiz our of bordom or because you're actually interested?</h2>
            <div class = "custom-margin">
                <div class="answer-choice">
                    <button class = "btn button-color" id="q6a1" data-question = "6"> out of bordeom </button>
                </div>
                <div class="answer-choice">
                    <button class = "btn button-color" id="q6a2" data-question = "6"> i'm interested   </button>
                </div>
                <p id="result"></p>
    
            </div>
        <div class = "center-align">
            <div id = "finish_btn">
                <button class = "btn-large button-color" id = "finish_button"> Next! </button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>